text: Hey Karen, I just noticed we're missing a font from the font package.
Can you send a request for Futura Medium Oblique? The Futura Oblique they gave is extra bold so it looks chunky.
<!channel> Do you happen to know what's the difference between "video streaming" and "embedded video" from the comp?
It's on the PDF with all the specs if that helps.

<@U02618EV1> I believe the only difference is that in the “lite” version of the app, we’re only including video files for the first video in the campaign and the others will be streaming or only show poster frame images if the user if offline

Thanks <@U02613K0X>. Looks like that's the case. The comp was a bit confusing and I couldn't tell whether they expected these 2 video boxes to have the same behavior or not (outside of displaying vids from diff sources).
